OL,3,CGloucestershire mother found guilty
OL,4,Cafter holding woman hostage for 25
OL,5,Cyears
OL,7,FA woman was imprisoned by a
OL,8,FGloucestershire mother in a suburban
OL,9,Fhome for a quarter of a century, a
OL,10,Fcourt's been told.
OL,12,FAmanda Wixon, 56, from Tewkesbury,
OL,13,Ftook in her victim, her friend's
OL,14,Fdaughter, in 1997. She was finally
OL,15,Ffreed in March 2021 after Wixon's son
OL,16,Fcalled the police.
OL,18,FA jury at Gloucester Crown Court found
OL,19,FWixon guilty of six charges, including
OL,20,Fcompulsory labour, false imprisonment
OL,21,Fand assault.
