OL,3,CGloucestershire mother found guilty
OL,4,Cafter holding woman hostage for 25
OL,5,Cyears
OL,7,FFor more than two decades she refused
OL,8,Fto allow the woman out, locking the
OL,9,Fdoors and windows. Wixon also forced
OL,10,Fher victim to look after her children,
OL,11,Fassaulted her and forced her to clean
OL,12,Fthe house.
OL,14,FThe trial at Gloucester Crown Court
OL,15,Fheard the victim, who ITV News is not
OL,16,Fnaming, made voice notes about her
OL,17,Fordeal. She was forced to live in
OL,18,Funsanitary conditions.
