OL,7,FWixon shaved her victim's head, hit
OL,8,Fher with a broom, forced washing up
OL,9,Fliquid down her throat and stamped on
OL,10,Fher victim, the prosecution alleged.
OL,12,FWixon denied two counts of compulsory
OL,13,Flabour, one count of false
OL,14,Fimprisonment and four assault charges.
OL,16,FGiving evidence, neighbours said they
OL,17,Fwent for years without seeing the
OL,18,Fvictim. One described her as looking
OL,19,F'like something from a concentration
OL,20,Fcamp'.
