OL,3,CGloucestershire mother found guilty
OL,4,Cafter holding woman hostage for 25
OL,5,Cyears
OL,7,F"When she was rescued from the
OL,8,Faddress, she went to see a doctor who
OL,9,Fsaid she was malnourished", said Det
OL,10,FSgt Alex Pockett of Gloucestershire
OL,11,FPolice.
OL,13,F"She had scars on her, on her lips.
OL,14,FAnd she had calluses on her feet from
OL,15,Fthe amount of time she spent on her
OL,16,Fhands and knees cleaning."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
