OL,7,F"She'd be sweeping up. She would clean
OL,8,Fthe address. She'd be getting up early
OL,9,Fto ensure that the kids would get
OL,10,Fready for school. And she would do
OL,11,Flots of menial tasks around the house."
OL,13,FHe went on to say, "The victim was
OL,14,Ftreated horrendously over the 20 years
OL,15,Fthat she was in the address. While she
OL,16,Fwas there, she was assaulted numerous
OL,17,Ftimes. All she wanted to have was long
OL,18,Fhair. And she was constantly having
OL,19,Fher hair cut short.
