OL,3,CGloucestershire mother found guilty
OL,4,Cafter holding woman hostage for 25
OL,5,Cyears
OL,7,F"She wasn't fed properly. She wasn't
OL,8,Feating properly. There were numerous
OL,9,Fassaults throughout the course of the
OL,10,Fperiod of time that she was in the
OL,11,Faddress. She was hit with a broom. She
OL,12,Fhad washing up liquid put in the
OL,13,Fmouth."
OL,15,FThe court heard the woman moved into
OL,16,FWixon's home in 1996 or 1997 when she
OL,17,Fwas in her late teens. Her parents
OL,18,Fwere friends with Wixon and knew she
OL,19,Fwas there.
